project.name: Ingres CAFÉ
project.description: Ingres Consolidated Application Foundation for Eclipse (CAFÉ) is an award winning Java application development tool that accelerates and simplifies development with Java. Ingres CAFÉ is an open source community-contributed project that eliminates the time-consuming tasks of acquiring, installing, and configuring the many components developers need in a Java application development environment. Ingres CAFÉ delivers a "one click and code" solution for Java development, bringing together leading open source products. Given that they are built on the Eclipse open source integrated development environment and Ingres Database, the applications can scale from the desktop to the data center without modification.
